feed.title: The Off Ended Podcast
feed.author: Michael
feed.description: Join the fearless crew of "The Off Ended Podcast" as we tackle a brutal range of topics, from the forbidden to the outrageous. Get ready for an unfiltered experience as 2Jz Da Grown Folk DJ, Mountain Mike, and M.O. dive headfirst into discussions that are bound to make even the boldest squirm.

items.title: Ep. 3 - What's up with these Aircraft?
items.author: Michael
items.description: On this episode of The Off Ended Podcast, the gentlemen of the mountain discuss snow, tariffs, and the aircraft disasters that have been happening as of late.
items.content: On this episode of The Off Ended Podcast, the gentlemen of the mountain discuss snow, tariffs, and the aircraft disasters that have been happening as of late.

items.author: Michael
items.description: The first time back at it in 2025! Today the gentlemen discuss the tragedy in New Orleans, the Steam Deck and the loss of 2Jz bracelet.
